<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7ab29944-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s9571"><num value="9571">§ 9571.</num><heading> Purpose</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Under Secretary shall establish the Minority Business Enterprises Advisory Council (referred to in this subchapter as the “Council”) to advise and assist the Agency.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7ab29945-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/117/58/dK/tV/s100501">Pub. L. 117–58, div. K, title V, § 100501</ref>, <date date="2021-11-15">Nov. 15, 2021</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/135/1463">135 Stat. 1463</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
